  "insecure-registries": [
    "your-repo:8082",
    "your-repo:8083"
  ],
  "disable-legacy-registry": true
}You have to restart the daemon after setting this (sudo systemctl restart docker).Now we have to authenticate your machine to the repo with:docker login -u admin -p admin123 your-repo:8082
docker login -u admin -p admin123 your-repo:8083This will create an entry in~/.docker/config.json:{
